data.description: HUGE PRICE IMPROVEMENT!! Welcome to this newly built Meritage home in the desirable Nolen Farm subdivision. Energy Star Certified for efficiency. Conveniently located just minutes from Historic Downtown Belmont, shopping, and restaurants. Meticulously maintained 4 bedroom, AND office. 3 full baths and a powder room for guests. Spacious laundry room located on the main level. Large primary bedroom with walk-in closet, tray ceilings and en-suite situated on the main level. And 2 additional bedrooms sharing a jack-n-Jill full bath. Gorgeous kitchen open to the living area makes for great entertaining space. The floor plan is very versatile and well designed giving much privacy for the entire family. Upstairs you have a bedroom with a full bath AND a loft area for gathering. This would be ideal for the older ones wanting their own space! The outside offers an extended patio and a fully fenced backyard. This house is move in ready and waiting for it's new owner.
